{"tid":1592272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵成功為閘機爭取茄汁","createTime":"2019-09-24T13:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T14:19:36.000Z","uid":48040,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1128b6e216c30d44495249a19e4ce67d2eef2365","tid":1592272,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:56:22.000Z","msg":"港鐵唔卑人跳閘，請埋大堆雇傭兵，一個學生哥跳下閘都搞到出防暴。<br />\n哇！好威威啊！<br />\n好啦，現在如港鐵所願，跳閘的確少咗。但係，唔跳閘唔係因為大家驚，而係大家選擇更加大殺傷力的辦法：喂閘機食茄汁。<br />\n假如問港鐵，係跳閘的影響大，定係閘機食茄汁影響大？唔使問都是係食茄汁啦。所以港鐵千方百計制止大家跳閘，其實只會適得其反，令自己付出更加大的代價。<br />\n呢個世界能量不滅。大家對港鐵的怒氣唔會因為你禁止跳閘而消失的。呢股憤怒的能量一定會轉化成為其他的形式。<br />\n但問題係班有權有勢的人，從來都唔會明白呢個道理。他們連最基本的&ldquo;能量不滅&rdquo;定律都唔明白，一味只懂得對民怨進行打壓。當民怨累積突破臨界點之後，等待當權者的只有滅亡的命運。<br />\n林鄭唔係好鍾意去探望慰問閘機咩？唔該去睇下個D食飽茄汁的閘機，好好想想這個道理吧。"},{"pid":"76d73e48082be07f79bec80b37831d9ef61967fc","tid":1592272,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"30cc4a4ad72e6444760952ee829ba983c526a89b","tid":1592272,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">國&hearts;際&hearts;戰&hearts;線&hearts;需&hearts;要&hearts;你</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RH29z9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRH29z9Z.jpg&h=787fa8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">☆</span>Tg channel 在此 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUi3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=8671f08b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a> <span style=\"color: gold;\">☆</span>"},{"pid":"1edd1291e630cce4eef4e2ef2229b4a1d22a1c29","tid":1592272,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:01:56.000Z","msg":"聽講月台幕門都幾貴下"},{"pid":"fba47395d6b13108006f6e56a0dde4bef9e182b3","tid":1592272,"uid":310982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:03:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b17674abc34a10346c0b9caf980bf8ad0e66a949","tid":1592272,"uid":312526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:05:42.000Z","msg":"等佢人少d又跳番"},{"pid":"689f02b4df62cd1e68ff294e93b77ff92cdb409c","tid":1592272,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:19:36.000Z","msg":"有金屬既地方都玩下茄汁"}]}